# zice-core

- Register routes in `internal/api/router.go` in the correct tier: public, protected (`middleware.Auth`), or tenant (`middleware.Tenant`).
- Use `internal/api/response` for `{data, error, meta}` envelopes.
- New entities: domain model → handler → router → migration + RLS → tests → `make check`.
- Migrations: `supabase/migrations/` with sequential timestamps; include RLS in the same file when adding tables.

Repo `AGENTS.md` (after `make sync-agent-docs`) has route and middleware details.
